outlined.description: Styles the rangepicker as an outlined text field. (labels or placeholders required)

labels.description: A text caption or description for the rangepicker, which use the start and end input's `placeholder` attribute instead.

placeholders.description: The placeholder attribute of the start and end <input>.

disabled.description: Styles the rangepicker as a disabled text field.

disable-range-plugin.description: Disables the flatpickr rangePlugin and use two `<ui-datepicker>` instead.
